task:    Phase 2 Task 3
files:   project/ingest/parse_filing.py, resources/artifacts/Changes.md
details: First deprecation fix (parsing_instruction -> system_prompt) was mechanically valid but semantically wrong: system_prompt replaces LlamaParse's internal default prompt wholesale (library docs: may impact accuracy), whereas the original parsing_instruction was additive. system_prompt_append is the parameter that actually preserves that additive behavior. Caught by the task reviewer, not self-discovered -- exactly the kind of subtle parameter-swap risk a second set of eyes exists for. Fixed and re-verified with a live smoke test using an actual 2-row financial table (not just a trivial paragraph), confirming atomic table extraction -- this task's core guarantee -- still holds. Recorded in Changes.md with the corrected reasoning.
